  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1971438/" class="title-link">闺训千字文和改良女儿经</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1971438"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/Paradox1986/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2975432-107.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Paradox1986/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Pipi</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-04-18"
      class="main-meta">2009-04-18 23:19:16</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1971438_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      女人遵循闺训千字文和改良女儿经的前提是，男有受三字经、千字文、弟子规等的教导。也就是说，娶个好媳妇儿的前提自身修养就得好，反之亦然。虽然是现代社会了，该归回的还是要回归。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1971438/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1971438_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1971438_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










